HEADWORD: Forslack
<hw>For*slack"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>for-</ets> + <ets>slack</ets> to neglect.]</ety> <def>To neglect by
idleness; to delay or to waste by sloth.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

